---
const whatsappUrl = 'https://wa.me/34623926731?text=Hola%20Natalia%2C%20quiero%20agendar%20una%20sesi%C3%B3n%20y%20recibir%20m%C3%A1s%20informaci%C3%B3n.';
---

<section id="inicio" class="relative overflow-hidden px-4 pb-16 pt-36 md:px-8 md:pt-40">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-stretch gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="reveal space-y-7">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-brand-700">Psicóloga General Sanitaria en Málaga y online</p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-5xl leading-tight text-warm-900 md:text-7xl">
        Encuentra tu bienestar emocional,
        <span class="relative italic text-brand-700">
          en un lugar seguro
          <svg viewBox="0 0 180 16" class="absolute -bottom-3 left-0 w-full text-accent-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M2 10c28 8 54-8 82-8 31 0 61 13 94 8" stroke-linecap="round" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        y libre de juicios.
      </h1>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-100 bg-white/80 p-4 text-warm-800 shadow-soft">
        <p class="font-semibold">Natalia, Psicóloga General Sanitaria y Terapeuta EMDR</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Ansiedad | Autoestima | Relaciones</p>
        <p class="text-sm">Trauma | Apego | Gestión Emocional</p>
        <p class="text-sm">Infertilidad | Embarazo | Postparto | Crianza</p>
        <p class="text-sm">Terapia individual y de pareja</p>
        <p class="text-sm">Presencial en Málaga y online</p>
      </div>

      <p class="max-w-xl text-center text-lg leading-relaxed text-warm-700 md:text-left">
        Acompañamiento psicológico para comprender el origen de tu malestar, desarrollar herramientas prácticas y construir un camino sólido hacia tu bienestar emocional.
      </p>

    </div>

    <div class="reveal relative flex h-full flex-col items-center justify-center gap-7">
      <div class="absolute -left-6 -top-6 h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-brand-300/50 blur-3xl animate-float"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-4 h-44 w-44 rounded-full bg-accent-300/50 blur-3xl animate-float"></div>

      <div class="relative h-[280px] w-[280px] md:h-[360px] md:w-[360px]">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden rounded-full ring-4 ring-white shadow-card-hover">
          <img
            src="/natalia-porras-foto-nueva.jpg"
            alt="Natalia Porras, psicóloga en Málaga"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover object-top"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-warm-900/72 via-warm-900/28 to-transparent px-8 pb-9 pt-20 text-center text-white">
            <p class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl">Natalia Porras</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-warm-100">Psicología</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img
          src="/butterfly-logo.png"
          alt="Logo mariposa Natalia Porras"
          class="absolute -right-2 -top-2 h-14 w-14 rounded-full border border-brand-200 bg-white/95 object-contain p-2 shadow-soft md:h-16 md:w-16"
        />

      </div>

      <div class="w-full max-w-[440px] space-y-4 rounded-2xl border border-brand-100 bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-soft md:max-w-[560px] md:p-6">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <a class="btn-primary" href={whatsappUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Reservar por WhatsApp</a>
          <a class="btn-outline" href="#servicios">Ver servicios</a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-brand-100 bg-white/70 p-4 text-center md:min-h-[112px] md:content-center">
            <p class="font-display text-2xl text-brand-700">Adultos</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-warm-700">Y adolescentes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-brand-100 bg-white/70 p-4 text-center md:min-h-[112px] md:content-center">
            <p class="font-display text-2xl text-brand-700">Parejas</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-warm-700">Acompañamiento vincular</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-brand-100 bg-white/70 p-4 text-center md:min-h-[112px] md:content-center">
            <p class="font-display text-2xl text-brand-700">Online</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-warm-700">Y presencial en Málaga</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
